<h3>Exploring Gameplay in Tealerland</h3>
Tealerland sets you in the role of David Artel, tasked with delving into the mysteries of his brother Teal’s disappearance. This survival-based horror game requires players to navigate through the park’s underground <strong>control facility from midnight until dawn</strong>, avoiding or trapping five hostile animatronics.
<ul>
 	<li><strong>Survive the Night</strong>: Traverse through three main locations: the office, the control room, and the hallway.</li>
 	<li><strong>T-Lure System</strong>: Utilize the parts of the T-Lure animatronic to attract and trap hostile robots in storage rooms, managing its integrity to avoid fatal errors.</li>
 	<li><strong>Dynamic Interaction</strong>: Repair and interact with various park systems to enhance your chances of survival.</li>
</ul>
